<h2>CORPORATE GIFT CARD ORDERS</h2>

<p>Londonderry Gift Cards make excellent gifts for business leaders looking for results. They offer the perfect solution to employee bonuses, sales and performance award incentives, as well as corporate gifts. We will be happy to accept your corporate credit card, or with pre-approval, your company cheque. For more information on the benefits of Londonderry&rsquo;s Corporate Gift Card program, please contact the Londonderry Marketing at 780-475-9266.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<h2>LOST, STOLEN OR DAMAGED GIFT CARDS</h2>

<p>If a Gift Card is lost, stolen or damaged, the Cardholder may request a replacement card if the cardholder presents the original receipt for the purchase of the Gift Card or the damaged Gift Card in the case of a damaged Gift Card. Any replacement Gift Card will be issued and activated in the amount of the available balance of the Gift Card Account at the time when the replacement card is issued. No fee will be charged for this.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

